# MoodConnect

MoodConnect is a simple web platform that allows users to share their emotions anonymously and view how others are feeling in real-time.

## Features
- Share your mood instantly
- View moods from other users
- Clean and minimal UI
- Anonymous interaction

## Tech Stack
- HTML, CSS, JavaScript

## Future Improvements
- Add authentication
- Real-time database (Firebase)
- Mood analytics

## Purpose
This project is built to explore how simple platforms can help people express emotions and feel connected.
